node.text:
Sounds like Starliner will not launch on Friday! It seems like they're preparing to roll the Atlas V rocket back from the launch site. This is likely due to the #Nauka issues at the @iss . Next available launch days are August 3 and 4! Credit @boeing and source Eric Berger
